  <summary date="2022-06-24T21:48:51Z" status="Introduced in House">We're Not Paying You To Break Our Laws Act

This bill prohibits making federal funds available to pay for any settlement agreement in any civil action brought as a result of actions taken to enforce the April 6, 2018, Department of Justice memorandum pertaining to the prosecution of cases of improper entry into the United States.</summary>
